## Audience Targeting Workflow

Define effective targeting strategy:

- [ ] 1. Objective alignment: Match targeting to campaign goals ({{campaign_objective}})
- [ ] 2. Audience definition: Define primary and secondary targets
- [ ] 3. Platform selection: Choose platforms that reach {{target_audience}}
- [ ] 4. Targeting parameters: Set demographics, interests, and behaviors
- [ ] 5. Lookalike modeling: Identify seed audiences for expansion
- [ ] 6. Exclusions: Define who NOT to target ({{exclusion_criteria}})

## Inputs
- Campaign objective: {{campaign_objective}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
